" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li></ul></div></div><a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/bergamo-teatro-donizetti-il-furioso-allisola-di-san-domingo/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/bergamo-teatro-donizetti-il-furioso-allisola-di-san-domingo/#respond"><span class="leave-reply" style="color:#363636 !important;">Leave a reply</span></a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/bergamo-teatro-donizetti-il-furioso-allisola-di-san-domingo/&amp;media=http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/GFR0042-1024x681.jpg&amp;description=Bergamo,%20Teatro%20Donizetti:%20&#8220;Il%20furioso%20all&#8217;isola%20di%20San%20Domingo&#8221;" target="_blank"><i class="icon-pinterest"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-fb" title="Share on Facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/bergamo-teatro-donizetti-il-furioso-allisola-di-san-domingo/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-twitter" title="Share on Twitter"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Bergamo,%20Teatro%20Donizetti:%20&#8220;Il%20furioso%20all&#8217;isola%20di%20San%20Domingo&#8221;&amp;url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/10/bergamo-teatro-donizetti-il-furioso-allisola-di-san-domingo/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-gplus" title="Share on Google Plus"><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.gbopera.i